        <details class="card">
          <summary><strong>How do I change colors and fonts?</strong></summary>
          <p>Edit the <code>:root</code> CSS variables at the top of this file. Swap the font-family in <code>body</code>.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="card">
          <summary><strong>Where do form submissions go?</strong></summary>
          <p>By default this uses <a href="https://formspree.io/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Formspree</a>. Replace the <code>data-endpoint</code> on the form with your own endpoint (e.g., serverless function, Mailchimp, etc.).</p>
        </details>
        <details class="card">
          <summary><strong>Can I add analytics?</strong></summary>
          <p>Yes. Add your script (e.g., Plausible or GA4) before <code>&lt;/body&gt;</code>. This template ships with no external JS by default.</p>
